    None

@EndNode

@Node CmdLineOptions "CmdLineOptions"

  Command Line Options
  ====================

    Full File Name (no path)
    File Name (with no .extension)
    File Extension (with no leading .)
    [NOUSER] (to enable quiet mode!)

@EndNode

